title: E332 Christmas Friends

description:
Theo talks about living in a new home, a recent stand up set, and takes some suggestions of senior quotes for last weeks caller Zachary.

He also checks in with a single mother who was nominated by a listener, and takes voicemails from some people struggling with some issues.
